channel.title: I need a run.bat file for my client [317]
channel.description:
hi, I need a run.bat code for my client runner. Mine doesn't seem to be working. Don't ask for the error because it doesnt do anything. I have jdk1.6.0_26 and here is my run.bat code.
[code]@echo off cd Java Files @title Run START JAVAW -Xmx500m EGUI[/code]
I know this is pretty much spoonfeeding, but please. someone, just give me their client runner. :)
